# Defensive: never push secrets or session state even if nested
**/.env
**/.wwebjs_auth/
**/.wwebjs_cache/

# Claude Code worktrees and session metadata.
# These get created automatically by `claude` and must never be committed:
# accidentally tracking a worktree directory leaves a gitlink (mode 160000)
# without a matching .gitmodules entry, which breaks `git submodule update`
# on any clone — including Cloudflare Pages, which always runs it.
.claude/
